                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black">GATHER REAL DATA</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-gray-800">Team members allocate points to show how strongly they feel about each option, revealing true priorities.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex gap-6 items-start">
              <div class="h-12 w-12 flex-none bg-black text-white flex items-center justify-center">
